## Formal syntax

{{CSSSyntax}}

## Examples

### Fixing a mask image to the viewport

```css
body {
  -webkit-mask-image: url('images/mask.png');
  -webkit-mask-attachment: fixed;
}
```

## Specifications

Not part of any standard.

