### Applying a bottom border

#### HTML

```html
<div>
  This box has a border on the bottom side.
</div>
```

#### CSS

```css
div {
  border-bottom: 4px dashed blue;
  background-color: gold;
  height: 100px;
  width: 100px;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-align: center;
}
```

