{{csssyntax}}

## Examples

### HTML

```html
<p>Firefox rocks!</p>
<p class="variant">Firefox rocks!</p>
```

### CSS

```css
@font-feature-values "Leitura Display Swashes" {
    @swash { fancy: 1 }
}

p {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.variant {
  font-family: Leitura Display Swashes;
  font-variant-alternates: swash(fancy);
}
```

### Result

