## Formal syntax

{{csssyntax}}

## Examples

### Setting minimum block size for vertical text

#### HTML

```html
<p class="exampleText">Example text</p>
```

#### CSS

```css
.exampleText {
  writing-mode: vertical-rl;
  background-color: yellow;
  min-block-size: 200px;
}
```

